text: Bağbanlı is a village and municipality in the Quba Rayon of Azerbaijan. It has a population of 1,562. == Climate == This region of Azerbaijan has a temperate climate..The temperature of Bağbanlı is 12.0 °C on average. August is typically the warmest month. ==References== Category:Populated places in Quba District (Azerbaijan)
title: Bağbanlı, Quba
